messages.content: Q: What did one leaf say to the other?  A: I'm feeling a bit 'rusty'!
The joke is that 'rusty' is a pun since the leaf is feeling a bit rusty -- get it?
Q: What did the ocean say to the wave?  A: Nothing, it just waved!
The joke is that 'waved' is a pun since the ocean didn't say anything, it just waved!
